Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:26.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:31.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:37.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:44.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:44.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:47.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:53.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:53.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:58.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:04.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:04.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:11.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:15.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:15.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:20.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:25.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:25.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:31.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:31.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:36.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:42.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:42.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:47.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:47.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:52.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:55.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:57.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:00.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:00.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:06.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:06.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:11.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:11.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:17.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:17.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:25.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is rushing to Navy HQ \Nto rescue his brother, Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is waiting to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the world's \Ngreatest pirate – Whitebeard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has finally appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the Navy HQ in Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cracked the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A seaquake! He's distorting the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still wanna run wild,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run as wild as you want\N on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you people call him Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he calls us "sons."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all hated by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's just a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:05:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Force That Could Destroy the World! \NThe Power of the Tremor-Tremor Fruit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to go but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who told you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who told him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we put you \Nthrough so much, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody in this world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to someone \Nwho messes with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let anybody who \Nhurts you get away with it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on us! We will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourselves, Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought this upon ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this side, we, The Warlords, \Nthe Navy's greatest powers--3 admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a hundred thousand elite soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that side, there are \Nthe Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and more than 40 allied ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how do you wanna do it, Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna be on the sideline as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you just came to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rowdy men everywhere \Nand I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is also a man but he is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm praying for you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is receding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is flying backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really smooth just two minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why all of the sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My waterworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Finally it stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went back a good distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when we can get \Nto Marineford like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hurry up? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get there before Ace's execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Luffy-kun. We'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll-y roll-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think your Fish-Man Karate can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you gonna call out \Nwhale sharks to help again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who are you depending on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said we'll make it! So we'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He said we'll make it! So we'll make it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stick around here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your dream to \Nbecome the King, Captain Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the time is right, \NI'm sure that there'll be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's too early, \Nthen I'll just wait for the right timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're gonna just give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, can't you see his \Nmagnificent confidence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It doesn't look like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call "perfect composure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got the regal presence\N to become the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that miracles don't happen that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is nothing I can do but wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could this be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The miracle that  you were\N talking about is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's happening \Nbut this is it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see it, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is calling me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying "come and become the King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so great! Like no other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! It seems like we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've quieted down all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they waiting for Whitebeard's command?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water level is rising again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the ground rumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seaquake that he set up before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in the form of tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tremor-Tremor Fruit \Nmade him a quake man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Newgate aka Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that our superior forces \Nwill guarantee us victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could well fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that man has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beginning! The war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The invaders: a fleet of 47 ships \Nfrom the New World led by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defenders: the 2 greatest\N forces of the Government--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy HQ and The Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who wins and who loses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the times will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:16:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly is the legendary monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Age!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You young squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Kuzan did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole bay is frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships can't move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have the greatest force of the \NNavy HQ--the admirals--on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be  \Nafraid of the Whitebeards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:18:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Destroy the Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a good foothold now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them what we're capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commanders came out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mount a counter-offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the 5th division \Ncommander - Flower Sword Vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alert, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all mighty soldiers - \Nnot just the commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got it, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have ice in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my blood is burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shoot them up and invade the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here come the vice admirals of the Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so rare to see all of them \Ntogether at the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when they have \Nthe Buster Call. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when it comes to Pops and us, \Nit won't work that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuru-san, why don't you stand back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it up to us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have some tea or something\N from a comfortable distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk smart to me, fledglings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no safe place even if \NI back up to the end of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the ship to the ice gorge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trounce them all and get to the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be happy to give our lives for Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not scared of the Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Squard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:21:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Warlord on the move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The capricious "Hawk-Eye" \Nseems like he's willing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to figure \Nout the true distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...between us and that man who \Nseems like right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even very skilled soldiers would \Ntremble and freeze from fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just by looking into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is truly a "Hawk-Eye" as he is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's every swordsman's dream \Nto cross swords with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he is assumed to be \Nthe strongest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the instinct of swordsmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Black Sword\N that everybody's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's Black Sword "Night!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the 12 highest \Ngrade swords in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its dark blade edge has an irregular \Ntemper line and a double clove pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a noted sword suitable \Nfor the greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hawk-Eye!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mihawk and Kizaru launch \Ntheir attacks on Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In response, the Whitebeard commanders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fight back using their own powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the unpredictable battle rages,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Akainu finally unleashes \Nhis incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An All-Consuming Inferno!! \NAdmiral Akainu's Power!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
